data.description:
This beautiful rental property has 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths spread across two spacious stories, providing plenty of room for comfortable living. The home features modern finishes and appliances, making it move-in-ready for you and your family. The open-concept living and dining areas are perfect for entertaining guests, and the bedrooms offer plenty of space for rest and relaxation. Located in a desirable neighborhood, you'll enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment.

$75 Application fee per person age 18 living in the home and 
 Security deposit is due when the application is turned in.

Renter's Insurance is required

We do a complete background check and verify income. You will need to provide a government-issued ID such as a Driver's License and a Social Security Card.

First month's rent is due at Move-In.

You must make 3x the rent 
Provide 3 most recent paycheck stubs
No broken leases or evictions
Felonies are reviewed on a case by case basis

In addition to monthly rent you are required to pay $50 a month for air filter replacement.
